author: Timothy Rapp
title: Ravens' Orlando Brown Jr.: 'I'm a Little Worried' NFL Season Will Be Canceled
description: Baltimore Ravens offensive lineman Orlando Brown Jr. told reporters Thursday he was concerned there might not be a 2020  NFL  season due to the COVID-19 pandemic, according to Jamison Hensley of ESPN...
content:
Phelan M. Ebenhack/Associated Press
Baltimore Ravens offensive lineman Orlando Brown Jr. told reporters Thursday he was concerned there might not be a 2020 NFL season due to the COVID-19 pandemic, according to Jamison Hensley of ESPN.
